      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., validation metric M) computed with uncertainty bounds for hemolysis index at all validation operating points; systematic bias identified and bounded.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index predictions deviate from experimental measurements by 18–42% across tested operating points. Validation metric computed but systematic over-prediction bias is not bounded by UQ intervals. Achieved level 2 is substantially below required level 4."
