      "rationale": "Two turbulence models (SST k-omega, realizable k-epsilon) were compared; SST k-omega selected. Hemolysis constitutive law sensitivity was not assessed across alternative power-law parameterizations. Model form uncertainty is not formally bounded. Achieved level 2 is well below required level 5."
