      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters must have documented sources with uncertainty distributions; Monte Carlo propagation must demonstrate that input uncertainty is bounded and does not dominate hemolysis index prediction error.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed on 6 of 11 identified uncertain input parameters. Blood viscosity, RBC fragility index, and inlet velocity profile shape were excluded from UQ due to lack of distribution data. Input uncertainty contribution is partially characterised; achieved level 2 is below required level 5."
